name: Cube Master: Escape levels 1
description:
Cube Master : Escape levels 1, First game developed by ODC games (Orgems Developement Company) made in unity the first version of this game contain 20 levels to play. The goal is to reach the green cube without falling (dying) this version is completely free to play. 

So make sure to enjoy playing this game , join our discord server and have fun !
